---
import Default from '../layouts/Default.astro';

const title = 'Licence | TARIDE Foundation';
const description = 'Content licence and trademark notice.';
---

<Default title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="container-reading">

    <span class="page-eyebrow">Content licence</span>
    <h1 class="page-title">Licence</h1>

    <p class="page-lede">
      Text and figures on this site are released under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International licence (CC BY 4.0). You may share and adapt the material for any purpose, including commercially, with attribution to "Stichting TARIDE" and a link back to <a href="https://taride.org">taride.org</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Source repositories</h2>
    <p>
      The website source lives at <a href="https://github.com/TARIDE-org/website" rel="noopener" data-umami-event="outbound-click" data-umami-event-url="https://github.com/TARIDE-org/website">TARIDE-org/website</a>. The protocol specifications and supporting documents live at <a href="https://github.com/TARIDE-org/docs" rel="noopener" data-umami-event="outbound-click" data-umami-event-url="https://github.com/TARIDE-org/docs">TARIDE-org/docs</a>. The design system lives at <a href="https://github.com/TARIDE-org/design-system" rel="noopener" data-umami-event="outbound-click" data-umami-event-url="https://github.com/TARIDE-org/design-system">TARIDE-org/design-system</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Full text</h2>
    <p>
      The full licence text is available at <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" rel="noopener" data-umami-event="outbound-click" data-umami-event-url="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/">creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Trademarks</h2>
    <p>
      The TARIDE wordmark and bracket motif are trademarks of Stichting TARIDE. The licence above covers content but not the marks. Use of the marks in a way that suggests endorsement requires permission.
    </p>

  </div>
</Default>
